Dialogue: 150,0:00:05.79,0:00:09.70,Song Lyrics Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}♪ 给我那最爱的邮件♪ \N{\rENG_LYC}♪ Bring me the post that I love the most ♪
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我勒个去\N{\rENG}Dagnabit!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哟 包裹还没来吗? \N{\rENG}Yo! No package yet?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}包裹还没来\N{\rENG}No package yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我确确实实在"高贵男孩"\N{\rENG}I definitely ordered a pair of khakis
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}买了一条卡其裤\N{\rENG}from The Distinguished Boy.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在应该差不多送到了\N{\rENG}They should've been delivered by now.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 我是个高贵的男孩\N{\rENG}I'm a distinguished boy, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.65,0:00:28.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难道我配不上一条高贵的卡其裤吗\N{\rENG}Don't I deserve distinguished khakis?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}想来点儿这个吗? \N{\rENG}Want one of these instead?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不了 谢谢\N{\rENG}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.39,0:00:37.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它随时会到\N{\rENG}Any second now.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.29,0:00:39.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 邮递员先生 给我来份邮件\N{\rENG}Hey, Mr. Postman, bring me a post!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真他喵的\N{\rENG}Consarn it!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米还没来\N{\rENG}Still no Jamie.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.76,0:00:47.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不明白 他一直都很准时的\N{\rENG}I don't understand. He's usually so punctual.
Dialogue: 150,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.77,Song Lyrics Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}♪ 给我来份邮件\N{\rENG_LYC}♪ Bring me a post
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你不应该为了等什么邮件\N{\rENG}Hey, you shouldn't have to waste your whole day
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.21,0:00:58.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而浪费掉一整天\N{\rENG}waiting for some thing in the mail.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.45,0:01:00.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}把这罐魔法豆子带到市里\N{\rENG}Take this can of magic beans into town
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}换一个甜甜圈来吧\N{\rENG}and trade it for a donut!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在喝…豆子? \N{\rENG}You've been drinking... beans?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.32,0:01:08.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}豆子对心脏有好处\N{\rENG}They're good for the heart.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很遗憾 按照我的经验\N{\rENG}Unfortunately, I know from experience
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.46,0:01:13.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}大甜甜圈是不接受魔法豆付款的\N{\rENG}The Big Donut does not accept magic beans as currency.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.63,0:01:17.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但在我买甜甜圈的时候 你还会在这里等杰米的吧\N{\rENG}But you'd still wait for Jamie while I got us some donuts?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 为什么不呢\N{\rENG}Sure. Why not?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.31,0:01:21.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不在的时候我们会坚守阵地的\N{\rENG}We'll hold down the fort while you're gone.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Amethyst! Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看 我们在搭一座小房子--给螃蟹的房子! \N{\rENG}Look! We're building a tiny house -- for crabs!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}欢迎来到新家\N{\rENG}Welcome to your new home.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.41,0:01:32.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 它们看起来很喜欢\N{\rENG}Oh! They like it!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-谢啦 紫晶 -没关系\N{\rENG}-Thanks, Amethyst! -No prob!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给我带个熊爪包回来就好\N{\rENG}Just bring me back a bear claw!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}早啊 酸奶油\N{\rENG}Good morning, Sour Cream!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你今晚有锐舞表演吗? \N{\rENG}Putting on a big rave tonight?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 你是说传单\N{\rENG}Oh -- the fliers.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 这些是关于洋葱头的\N{\rENG}No, it's Onion.
Dialogue: 500,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.17,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs160\c&H240CE7&\bord0\shad0\frz7.232\pos(774,1008)}走失
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.20,0:01:54.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他已经失踪了好几天了\N{\rENG}He's been missing for a couple of days now.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我妈和黄爹已经开始担心了\N{\rENG}My mom and Yellowdad are starting to get worried.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你最近有见过他吗\N{\rENG}You haven't seen him around lately, have you?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.54,0:02:02.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没有 你有去树林里他最喜欢的地方找过吗\N{\rENG}No. Have you checked his favorite hiding spot in the woods?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然了\N{\rENG}Sure did.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那游乐场的自动售货机里呢\N{\rENG}What about inside the vending machine at Funland?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没找到\N{\rENG}No luck.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还费了我一块钱\N{\rENG}Blew a dollar checking, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.42,0:02:12.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那你家里最机密的那个房间呢\N{\rENG}What about that top-secret room inside your house?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.22,0:02:14.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你说他的办公室?  没有\N{\rENG}You mean his office? Of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我敢肯定他没事的\N{\rENG}Eh, I'm sure he's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果他跟小时候的我一样\N{\rENG}If he's anything like me when I was a kid,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他可能只是--我不确定--\N{\rENG}he's probably just -- I don't know --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在一个朋友家后院锐舞\N{\rENG}raving in a friend's backyard.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不管怎么说 我最好把剩下这些贴起来\N{\rENG}Anyway, I'd better hang the rest of these up.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能给拉尔斯和莎蒂一张吗\N{\rENG}Can you make sure Lars and Sadie get one of these?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想在大甜甜圈也贴一张\N{\rENG}I wanted to hang one up at The Big Donut,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不过它关门了\N{\rENG}but it's closed.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}关门了\N{\rENG}Closed?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}莎蒂噫噫噫噫噫\N{\rENG}Sadieeeeeee!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们肯定在这儿\N{\rENG}They have to be here.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道你们在干什么\N{\rENG}I know what you guys are doing.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们在休息室看恐怖电影\N{\rENG}You guys are watching scary movies in the break room,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正如你们不该做的那样\N{\rENG}like you're not supposed to be!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}开门啊\N{\rENG}Open up!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想要个甜甜圈\N{\rENG}I...want...a donut!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.17,0:03:08.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你是想破门而入还是怎样\N{\rENG}Hey! You trying to break in or something?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}巴布!  呃 不是\N{\rENG}Barb! Uh...no.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我 我只是在找拉尔斯和莎蒂\N{\rENG}I-I was just looking for Lars and Sadie.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但他们不在这里\N{\rENG}But they're not back here.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 你是怎么进去的\N{\rENG}Uh... how did you get in?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}作为一个好母亲 怎么说也得\N{\rENG}Well, what kind of mother would I be
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有自己女儿所有钥匙的备份啊\N{\rENG}if I didn't make a copy of all my daughter's keys?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是过来送莎蒂的午餐\N{\rENG}I only came over to drop off Sadie's lunch.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她昨晚不在家 所以我想我应该送到这儿\N{\rENG}She wasn't home last night, so I figured I'd bring it here.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这地方连人影都没\N{\rENG}But the place was completely empty.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许今天是什么面包师节之类的\N{\rENG}Maybe it's some sort of baker's holiday.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}肯定不是个国家节日\N{\rENG}It's certainly not a federal one.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}莎蒂昨晚没回家? \N{\rENG}Sadie never came home last night?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘛 她也算一个成人了\N{\rENG}Eh, she's an adult.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可能只是溜出去跟她男朋友\N{\rENG}Probably just snuck off
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}再来个岛屿探险之旅\N{\rENG}for another "island adventure" with her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那不可能\N{\rENG}That couldn't be.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们当时是要去聚会的\N{\rENG}They were going to go to a party together,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是拉尔斯一直没来\N{\rENG}but Lars never showed.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们离开时 莎蒂说她要回家\N{\rENG}And when me and Sadie left, she said she was going home.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.65,0:03:57.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而现在 酸奶油正到处寻找洋葱头\N{\rENG}And now Sour Cream is looking everywhere for Onion.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我正在等杰米的一个包裹\N{\rENG}And I was expecting a package today from Jamie,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但他--他一直没送来\N{\rENG}but he -- he never delivered it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个包裹\N{\rENG}A package?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是说一个大概这么大 两磅 也许四盎司的包裹吗\N{\rENG}You mean one about yea big, 2 pounds, maybe 4 ounces?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我高贵的卡其裤! \N{\rENG}My distinguished khakis!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那你看到杰米了吗? \N{\rENG}Did you see Jamie with them?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}今天早上看到了--\N{\rENG}I did this morning --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就在我派他去你那里之前\N{\rENG}just before sending him off to your place.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}巴布 形势也许非常严峻\N{\rENG}Barb, this might be serious.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我去看看能不能在木板道那里找到什么人\N{\rENG}I'll go see if I can find anyone on the boardwalk.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我到每家门前去找找堆积着的包裹\N{\rENG}I'll go check doorsteps for piled-up packages.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这样我们就知道还有谁失踪了\N{\rENG}Then we'll know if anyone else is missing.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}莎蒂 别怕 亲爱的\N{\rENG}Sadie! Don't worry, honey!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}妈妈来了 宝贝女儿\N{\rENG}Mama's comin' for ya, baby girl!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}祝好运\N{\rENG}Good luck.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米\N{\rENG}Jamie...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}洋葱头\N{\rENG}Onion...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Lars...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}莎蒂\N{\rENG}Sadie?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许他们都去度假了\N{\rENG}Maybe they're all on vacation?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 史蒂文\N{\rENG}No, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}无论是发生了什么 我都应该找到他们\N{\rENG}Whatever the case, it's up to me to find them.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.41,0:04:56.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米 洋葱头\N{\rENG}Jamie! Onion!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯 莎蒂\N{\rENG}Lars! Sadie!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-正在等待肯定我的挑战者\N{\rENG}Awaiting new challengers to validate me.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-来个人胖揍我一顿吧 拜托了\N{\rENG}Somebody, punch me! Please.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘛 酸奶油说的没错\N{\rENG}Well, Sour Cream was right --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}洋葱头不在自动售货机里\N{\rENG}Onion wasn't in the vending machine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其他人也不在\N{\rENG}And neither was anybody else.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是我爸爸吗\N{\rENG}Are you my dad?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊啊啊 一个宝石人\N{\rENG}Aaah! A Gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是我爸爸吗\N{\rENG}Are you my dad?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得找到我爸爸\N{\rENG}I need to find my dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不不 我不是\N{\rENG}N-No, I-I'm not.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等等一下\N{\rENG}W-W-Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别又让我陷入一个谜啊\N{\rENG}Don't leave me with another enigma!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的本体在她眼睛下方\N{\rENG}And the gem was under her eye --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们的左手边 她的右手边\N{\rENG}our right, her left.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有翅膀…没错\N{\rENG}And the wings and...yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想我把一个眼睛画大了\N{\rENG}I think I made one eye bigger than the other.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是跟着感觉走的\N{\rENG}I was going for a feeling.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说真的我连个圆都画不好\N{\rENG}Honestly, I can't even draw a circle.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 石榴 你只是画了你自己\N{\rENG}Okay, Garnet, you just drew yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我喜欢我自己\N{\rENG}Uh, I like me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.68,0:06:03.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 我想康妮是画的最像的\N{\rENG}Well, anyway, I think Connie was the closest.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢\N{\rENG}Thanks!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这真是浪费时间\N{\rENG}This was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们应该准备战斗\N{\rENG}We should be preparing for a fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不管她是谁 她都是来自母星的\N{\rENG}Whoever this is, she's from Homeworld.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她一定是来找我们的\N{\rENG}She's got to be here for us!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实并不是 她说她是来找她爸爸的\N{\rENG}She's not, though. She said she's looking for her dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥 她爸?\N{\rENG}What? Her dad?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这么多人都失踪了\N{\rENG}There are all these people missing.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说不定她爸也失踪了\N{\rENG}Maybe her dad's gone missing, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是宝石人没有爹啊\N{\rENG}But Gems don't have dads!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不合理\N{\rENG}This doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.77,0:06:30.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文就是个宝石人 他也有个爹\N{\rENG}Steven's a Gem, and Steven has a dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是没有其他像史蒂文这样的宝石人了\N{\rENG}There are no other Gems like Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你确定\N{\rENG}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们必须一探究竟\N{\rENG}We've got to get to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们应该分开行动\N{\rENG}We should split up and investigate.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}红宝石和蓝宝石\N{\rENG}Ruby and Sapphire!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 不是 我是说分成小队\N{\rENG}Uh, no. I meant split into teams.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦对\N{\rENG}Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴你自己一队 珍珠和紫晶 康妮和我一队\N{\rENG}Garnet with yourself, Pearl with Amethyst, and Connie with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}出发\N{\rENG}Let's go!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 你真的认为\N{\rENG}Connie, do you really think
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还可能有我这样的宝石人吗\N{\rENG}there could be another Gem like me?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘛 你懂宝石人懂得比我多\N{\rENG}Well, you know more about Gems than I do.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但没什么不可能 你就存在啊\N{\rENG}But it can't be impossible. You exist.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但她看起来没有人类血统\N{\rENG}She didn't look half human, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的皮肤是蓝色的…还有翅膀\N{\rENG}She was blue and...had wings.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许她是被收养的\N{\rENG}Well, what if she's adopted?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许她坠入一个大城市\N{\rENG}What if she crash-landed in the big city
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许她被一个拥有金子般的心的\N{\rENG}and she was taken in by a lonely millionaire
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.69,0:07:16.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}孤独的富翁收养了\N{\rENG}with a heart of gold?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还拥有万贯家产\N{\rENG}And a house of gold.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是有一天他去沙滩市出差\N{\rENG}But one day, he went on a business trip to Beach City
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}却再也没回来\N{\rENG}and he never came home.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这故事拍成电影我肯定会看的\N{\rENG}I guess I'd watch the movie of that.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者写成书\N{\rENG}Or read the book.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者两者皆非 因为它可能是真事儿 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Or neither, 'cause it could be reality, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真的这么认为\N{\rENG}You really think so?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.77,0:07:35.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 只有找到真相我们才能知道\N{\rENG}Hey, the only way to know is to find out.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对\N{\rENG}Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯 这儿有风\N{\rENG}Yup. There's wind.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}天啊\N{\rENG}Man.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我记得在这里和洋葱头他们玩\N{\rENG}I feel like I was just here
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}感觉就像昨天发生的事\N{\rENG}with Onion and all his friends.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他到底去哪了\N{\rENG}Where is he?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可怜的酸奶油 丢了他的弟弟\N{\rENG}Poor Sour Cream, missing his brother...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}巴布丢了她女儿\N{\rENG}and Barb missing her daughter --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}和她的邮差--\N{\rENG}and her mailman --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有这个宝石人丢了她的爸爸! \N{\rENG}and this new Gem missing her dad!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能理解一个人失去老爸的滋味\N{\rENG}I know what it's like to have your dad taken away.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她一定害怕极了\N{\rENG}She must be so scared.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你成功找回了你爸\N{\rENG}But you got your dad back.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你也一定能帮她找到\N{\rENG}And you'll solve this, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会一起找到\N{\rENG}We'll solve this -- together.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢 康妮\N{\rENG}Thanks, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好 让我们把这片树林翻个底朝天吧\N{\rENG}Okay. Let's turn these woods upside down.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}洋葱头\N{\rENG}Onion!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米\N{\rENG}Jamie!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.56,0:08:30.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在这儿给苔藓送包裹吗?\N{\rENG}You in here delivering packages to some peat moss?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.27,0:08:34.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 是那个宝石人\N{\rENG}Steven! It's the Gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她看起来和我画的一模一样\N{\rENG}She looks just like my drawing!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.47,0:08:40.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}过来这里 别怕 我们会帮你的\N{\rENG}Come on. You don't have to be afraid. We'll help you!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}跳进我怀里\N{\rENG}Jump down into my arms.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会接住你的\N{\rENG}My body will break your fall.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是我爸爸吗\N{\rENG}Are you my dad?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.55,0:08:51.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 我 我不是你爸\N{\rENG}No. I-I'm not your dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我们可以帮你找到你爸\N{\rENG}We can help you find your dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不是在找你爸\N{\rENG}I'm not looking for your dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在找我爸爸\N{\rENG}I'm looking for my dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.76,0:09:01.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得找到我爸爸\N{\rENG}I need to find my dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们…会帮你\N{\rENG}Well, we'll...help you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮\N{\rENG}Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 等等 小心啊\N{\rENG}Connie, wait! Be careful!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 你是康妮吗\N{\rENG}Connie. Are you Connie?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对 我是康妮\N{\rENG}Yes! I'm Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是--康妮 康妮是--朋友\N{\rENG}Me -- Connie. Connie -- friend.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石\N{\rENG}Topaz!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我找到了一个 我找到了一个\N{\rENG}I found one! I found one!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我找到了一个康妮\N{\rENG}I found a Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文\N{\rENG}Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮\N{\rENG}Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有一个宝石人\N{\rENG}Another Gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.51,0:09:51.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她 她劫持了所有人\N{\rENG}She -- She has everyone!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}放开他们\N{\rENG}Let them go!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮\N{\rENG}Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.63,0:10:13.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看着这些有机体蠕动的样子\N{\rENG}Look at those organics squirming around.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}把我的朋友还给我\N{\rENG}Give me back my friends!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别费神听那个史蒂文了\N{\rENG}Don't bother listening to that Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他不是我爸爸\N{\rENG}He's not my dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.38,0:10:34.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在我们只需要我爸爸 然后我们就走\N{\rENG}Now all we need is my dad, and we're out of here!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们居然派一个海蓝宝\N{\rENG}Can't believe they wasted an Aquamarine
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}浪费时间做这种任务\N{\rENG}on a job like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.76,0:10:41.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这太简单了 你都可以一个人完成了 托帕石\N{\rENG}It's so easy, you could have done it yourself, Topaz.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不可以带走他们\N{\rENG}You can't take them.
